    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>SACHS-Hilda. Age 89. Died quietly at her home, on Sunday, October 15. Beloved wife of Edgar Sachs. Loving mother of Stephen. She was a prolific writer and lyricist, a former member of the editorial staff of House &amp; Garden Magazine and a prominent and highly respected publicist in the Home Fashion Industry. Well beloved by all who knew her. Funeral services are private.</p>
      </block>
